Pat Tilapia Filets dry, place onto entr√©e style dinner plate and season with pepper. Combine soy sauce, sesame oil, ginger slices, green onions and cilantro, mix to incorporate and pour over top of Tilapia Filets. Wrap the entire preparation in plastic wrap, sealing tightly. Microwave for 4 minutes at high heat or until the fish is thoroughly cooked. Remove plastic wrap and enjoy.